ZH: 因果关系是世界上一切事物相互联系的根本原理。
EN: The law of cause and effect is the fundamental principle of interconnectedness in the world.

ZH: 因果报应是一种普遍存在的信念。
EN: The belief in the law of cause and effect is universal.

ZH: 我们应该明白，每一个行为都会产生相应的因果结果。
EN: We should understand that every action produces corresponding cause and effect results.

ZH: 只有了解因果关系，才能认清事物的本质。
EN: Only by understanding the law of cause and effect can we recognize the essence of things.

ZH: 人生的每一步都有因果相应。
EN: Every step in life has corresponding cause and effect.

ZH: 犯下的罪恶行为终将获得相应的因果报应。
EN: Evil deeds committed will eventually receive corresponding karmic retribution.

ZH: 宇宙之间的平衡完全取决于因果关系。
EN: The balance between the universe relies entirely on the law of cause and effect.

ZH: 每一个决定都会在之后产生因果效应。
EN: Every decision will have causal effects in the future.

ZH: 因果关系深入影响每一个生命的轨迹。
EN: The law of cause and effect deeply influences the trajectory of every life.

ZH: 对于伤害他人的行为，我们不应该忽略因果关系。
EN: We should not overlook the law of cause and effect when it comes to harming others.

ZH: 生命中的挫折可能是因果法则的一种显现。
EN: The setbacks in life may be a manifestation of the law of cause and effect.

ZH: 每个人选取的路途经过积极解析因果关系。
EN: Each person's chosen path involves actively interpreting the law of cause and effect.

ZH: 人们善待他人可以创造正面的因果关系。
EN: Treating others kindly can create positive cause and effect relationships.

ZH: 我们之间的关系是相互连接的因果。
EN: The relationship between us is a interconnected cause and effect.

ZH: 因果律定了每一个人的生命命运。
EN: The law of cause and effect determines the destiny of each person's life.

ZH: 了解因果法则有助于我们更好地改变自己的命运。
EN: Understanding the law of cause and effect helps us better change our destiny.

ZH: 因果关系的深度主导着宇宙的自然规律。
EN: The depth of cause and effect governs the natural laws of the universe.

ZH: 每个人的命运之路都离不开因果力量的推动。
EN: Every person's path of destiny cannot be separated from the driving force of cause and effect.

ZH: 种种原因导致我们与自然因果相联系。
EN: Various reasons lead us to be connected with the natural cause and effect.

ZH: 因果关系是永不停息的生命宇宙循环。
EN: The law of cause and effect is an unceasing cycle in the universe of life.
